<item>
            <title>[HBASE-3625] improve/fix support excluding Tests via Maven -D property</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-3625</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently the surefire plugin configuration defines the following exclusion:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
.
      &amp;lt;plugin&amp;gt;
        &amp;lt;groupId&amp;gt;org.apache.maven.plugins&amp;lt;/groupId&amp;gt;
        &amp;lt;artifactId&amp;gt;maven-surefire-plugin&amp;lt;/artifactId&amp;gt;
        &amp;lt;configuration&amp;gt;
          &amp;lt;forkMode&amp;gt;always&amp;lt;/forkMode&amp;gt;
          &amp;lt;includes&amp;gt;
            &amp;lt;include&amp;gt;**/Test*.java&amp;lt;/include&amp;gt;
          &amp;lt;/includes&amp;gt;
          &amp;lt;excludes&amp;gt;
            &amp;lt;exclude&amp;gt;**/*$*&amp;lt;/exclude&amp;gt;
          &amp;lt;/excludes&amp;gt;
        &amp;lt;/configuration&amp;gt;
      &amp;lt;/plugin&amp;gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;AFAICT the &apos;&lt;tt&gt;**&lt;b&gt;/&lt;/b&gt;*&lt;b&gt;$&lt;/b&gt;*&lt;/tt&gt;&apos; does not resolve to anything meaningful.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Adding support to exclude one or more tests via Maven property, i.e. &apos;&lt;tt&gt;-Dtest.exclude=&amp;lt;TESTCLASS&amp;gt;&lt;/tt&gt;&apos; would be useful.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;all&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
